cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: DPS 16/23DL Dynamic Purchasing System for International Higher Edcuation Student Recruitment to Atlantic Technological University
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: ATU wishes to establish a Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS) of Education Agents to support the recruitment of non-EU students across all campuses. All applicants who provide the information in the Qualification Questionnaire contained in Appendix 1, who clearly demonstrate they operate within this service area will be considered for admittance to the DPS.
